<h2 id="icons">Icons</h2>
<p>Icons illustrate actions, communicate status, indicate an interaction and
  draw attention to important information.</p>
<p>Icons can be added to components or paired with text. Avoid having icons as standalone as they may be interpreted differently by different users. It is important to ensure where an icon is used it matches the intended action.</p>
<p>The NSW Design System uses <a taget="_blank" href="https://fonts.google.com/icons?selected=Material+Icons">Material design</a> icons (filled versions) for an easily implementable and consistent user experience.</p>

