<h3>Accessibility</h3>
<p>Do:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Wrap icons within their interactive component</li>
  <li>Specify if an icon is decorative and informative by assigning the appropriate property. (Add code example)
  </li>
  <li>Use descriptive and meaningful titles for informative icons</li>
</ul>
<h3>Designing</h3>
<p>Icons used to build base components are included in the UI Kit. Base colour ranges are available and can be changed using the Variants panel in Figma. If you require additional icons, you can download them from <a href="https://fonts.google.com/icons?selected=Material+Icons">Material design   icons</a> and import where required.</p>
